            </encodings>
            <customized-tooltip show-buttons='false'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>About This Dashboard</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>This dashboard analyzes </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>global e-commerce sales data from a software retailer</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> offering subscriptions and add-ons across </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Analytics, Design, Collaboration, and AI products</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>.
The goal of the analysis is to </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>understand customer loyalty, revenue drivers, and the impact of channels and promotions on repeat purchasing behavior</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>The dashboard is designed to be </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>easy to read, insight-driven, and decision-focused</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>, enabling stakeholders to quickly answer key business questions around sales performance, customer retention, and pricing strategy.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Business Objectives</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>This dashboard aims to help stakeholders:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Track </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>sales and loyal customer growth over time</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Identify </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>channels that drive the most revenue and repeat customers</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Understand </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>which products and plans perform best</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Surface opportunities to </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>improve retention, revenue, and marketing effectiveness</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Customer Definition &amp; Loyalty Logic</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>A </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>customer</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> is identified using a unique Customer ID.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>A </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>loyal (repeat) customer</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> is defined as:</run>
                <run lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>A customer who has completed </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>more than one non-refunded order</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria' lmargin='600' rmargin='600'>.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Refunded orders are excluded from loyalty and repeat-purchase calculations to ensure accuracy.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Event &amp; Time Interpretation</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Event Date</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> represents the actual transaction or interaction time</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Signup Date</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> represents when the customer officially registered</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>All time-based trends (monthly sales, repeat behavior, time to second purchase) are calculated using </run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Event Date</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>.</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Key Metrics Explained</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Sales Metrics</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Total Revenue:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> Net revenue generated from non-refunded orders</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Orders:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> Unique completed purchases</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Average Order Value (AOV):</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> Revenue per order</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Quantity:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> Total Quantity sold</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Filters:</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Date: </run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>7, 14, 21, 30, 90, and Year To Date</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'>Metric Switch:</run>
                <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Cambria'> Revenue, Quantity, and Customers</run>
              </formatted-text>
            </customized-tooltip>
            <style>
              <style-rule element='mark'>
                <format attr='shape' value='info/warning.png' />
                <format attr='size' value='0.73563534021377563' />
              </style-rule>
            </style>
          </pane>
        </panes>
        <rows />
        <cols />
      </table>
